&lt;p style="text-align:center"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif"&gt;The Private Security/Investigator Policy Committee of the Board on Public Safety Standards and Training will hold a regular meeting on Tuesday, November 18, 2025, at 1:30 p.m., in the Governor Victor G. Atiyeh Boardroom at the Department of Public Safety Standards and Training (DPSST or Department) located at 4190 Aumsville Hwy SE, Salem, Oregon. For further information, please contact Juan Lopez at (503) 551-3167.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style="text-align:center"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style="margin-left:-0.25pt; text-align:center"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:times new roman,times,serif"&gt;**&lt;em&gt;To view the Private Security/Investigator Policy Committee's live-stream and other recorded videos, please visit DPSST&rsquo;s official YouTube page at &lt;a href="https://gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?data=05%7C02%7CSamantha.KOSSA%40stateoforegon.mail.onmicrosoft.com%7C426ef76ff49d439d59f108dc1d2504cb%7Caa3f6932fa7c47b4a0cea598cad161cf%7C0%7C0%7C638417292033690646%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C3000%7C%7C%7C&amp;amp;reserved=0&amp;amp;sdata=sh%2FUHpNq80FuoCGzlEPn%2B%2FOO00D82zaxjUk%2ByUIAZ8U%3D&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40DPSST%3Futm_medium%3Demail%26utm_source%3Dgovdelivery&amp;amp;utm_medium=email&amp;amp;utm_source=govdelivery" rel="noopener" target="_blank" title="Original URL: https://www.youtube.com/@DPSST?utm_medium=email&amp;amp;utm_source=govdelivery. Click or tap if you trust this link."&gt;https://www.youtube.com/@DPSST.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

