&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:18px"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Public record&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href="https://www.bentoncountyor.gov/lu-24-027-proposed-coffin-butte-landfill-expansion/"&gt;LU-24-027 Public Record&lt;/a&gt; is available on the County&rsquo;s website.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Recordings of the two nights of hearings before the Board of Commissioners can be viewed on the &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLxkQOCH37N7qo0QAxSSKwy_mi_HT4qnXV"&gt;County&rsquo;s YouTube channel&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
     &lt;li&gt;The &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8gUn448GzVU"&gt;Oct. 22 recording&lt;/a&gt; includes a presentation of the Planning Division Staff Report, a presentation by the applicant, verbal testimony by proponents of the expansion, testimony by government representatives and the beginning of testimony by opponents of the expansion.&lt;/li&gt;
     &lt;li&gt;The Oct. 23 recording includes the bulk of the testimony by opponents of the expansion. The meeting wrapped up with questions from the Commissioners to be addressed in the applicant's written rebuttal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For more information about the appeal hearing visit &lt;a href="https://www.bentoncountyor.gov/coffin-butte-landfill/"&gt;bentoncountyor.gov/coffin-butte-landfill&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style="font-family: &amp;quot;Optimistic 95&amp;quot;, system-ui, sans-serif; color: rgb(28, 43, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
