&lt;div class="_1mf _1mj" style="position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:inherit"&gt;After additional investigation, Rogers was arrested and lodged at the Lane County Jail on the following charges: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
