&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the America 250 Oregon Commission&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The mission of the America 250 Oregon Commission is to coordinate, provide guidance, and ensure that Oregon&rsquo;s official observance of the 250th anniversary of the founding of the United States is inclusive and shares the histories of Oregon&rsquo;s diverse populations, including the histories of the Indigenous peoples who have resided here since time immemorial. Learn more at &lt;a href="https://www.oregon250.org/"&gt;oregon250.org&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Oct. 27, 2025&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

