&lt;p&gt;ROSEBURG, Ore., Oct. 14, 2025 &mdash; The Roseburg Concert Chorale and Umpqua Community College are delighted to present &ldquo;Messiah&rdquo; by George Frederic Handel on November 21 at 7:00 p.m. at the Church of the Nazarene in Myrtle Creek, and on November 23 at 3:00 p.m. in Jacoby Auditorium. This iconic work, under the direction of Dr. Jason Heald, will include a seventy-five-voice choir with full orchestra. Tickets at While Away Books and admission at the door, $15.00 general admission, $10.00 seniors, and students admitted FREE. For more information, contact &lt;a href="mailto:music@umpqua.edu"&gt;music@umpqua.edu&lt;/a&gt; or 541-440-4691.&lt;/p&gt;

