&lt;div class="_1mf _1mj" style="position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:inherit"&gt;Heath&rsquo;s interest in the fire service started young&mdash;sparked by the classic TV show Emergency!. &ldquo;That led to Fire Explorers in high school, enlisting in the Air Force as a firefighter, and then becoming a civilian firefighter,&rdquo; he shared.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style="font-family: &amp;quot;Optimistic 95&amp;quot;, system-ui, sans-serif; color: rgb(28, 43, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;div class="_1mf _1mj" style="position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style="font-family: &amp;quot;Optimistic 95&amp;quot;, system-ui, sans-serif; color: rgb(28, 43, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;div class="_1mf _1mj" style="position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:inherit"&gt;He joined Lebanon Fire District as a volunteer in November 2023, transitioning to a full-time temporary firefighter in April 2024. Now, as a full-time member of the District, Heath says, &ldquo;It&rsquo;s an amazing opportunity! To be able to continue doing what I love with an amazing group of people has been outstanding.&rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style="font-family: &amp;quot;Optimistic 95&amp;quot;, system-ui, sans-serif; color: rgb(28, 43, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;div class="_1mf _1mj" style="position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style="font-family: &amp;quot;Optimistic 95&amp;quot;, system-ui, sans-serif; color: rgb(28, 43, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;div class="_1mf _1mj" style="position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:inherit"&gt;Heath acknowledges that the fire service comes with both challenges and rewards. &ldquo;Every firefighter will have moments, good and bad. That&rsquo;s why we lean on our brothers and sisters for support and motivation&mdash;it&rsquo;s why Fire, Police, EMS, and military have a bond that can last a lifetime.&rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style="font-family: &amp;quot;Optimistic 95&amp;quot;, system-ui, sans-serif; color: rgb(28, 43, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;div class="_1mf _1mj" style="position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style="font-family: &amp;quot;Optimistic 95&amp;quot;, system-ui, sans-serif; color: rgb(28, 43, 51); font-size: 14px; white-space-collapse: preserve; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"&gt;
&lt;div class="_1mf _1mj" style="position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:inherit"&gt;When asked about his mentors, Heath&rsquo;s answer was simple: &ldquo;Everyone&mdash;from the Chief to the newest firefighter. All have provided insight and guidance.&rdquo; He&rsquo;s proud of how quickly he&rsquo;s been able to contribute, saying, &ldquo;Being able to jump right in and help however I can has been deeply fulfilling&rdquo;. In his new role, Heath looks forward to &ldquo;motivating and guiding younger generations and helping them achieve their goals.&rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

