&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:14px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;On October 30, detectives from the Salem Police Department&rsquo;s Felony Crimes Unit, in partnership with the Violent Crimes Unit, Patrol Division, and loss prevention teams from TJ Maxx, Sierra, HomeGoods, and Burlington, conducted a targeted retail theft sting at the shopping center on Lancaster Drive NE. The operation was funded by the Oregon Department of Justice Organized Retail Theft Grant Program.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
