&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:14px"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;The Salem Police Traffic Team is leading the investigation and next of kin notification was completed.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:arial nova,arial nova_embeddedfont,arial nova_msfontservice,sans-serif"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
