&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
     &lt;li&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href="https://douglascountyor.gov/539/Board-of-Commissioners"&gt;Douglas County Board of Commissioners&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; and designated department officials will remain engaged and available to respond to any local emergencies, regardless of the holiday.&lt;/li&gt;
