     &lt;li&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://umpquavalleymuseums.org/"&gt;Umpqua River Lighthouse Museum&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; in Winchester Bay will be open for visitors on Thursday, November 27, 2025, for normal business hours.&lt;/li&gt;
