     &lt;li&gt;Even though the &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.dcso.com/"&gt;Douglas County Sheriff&rsquo;s Office&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; (DCSO) lobby entrance will be closed on Thursday, November 27, 2025, our Sheriff&rsquo;s Deputies, 911 communications and DCSO staff will continue to provide law enforcement protection and emergency assistance for our residents.&amp;nbsp; If you have an emergency, call 9-1-1.&amp;nbsp; If you need to reach dispatch for a non-emergency, call the DCSO non-emergency number at (541) 440-4471.&amp;nbsp; &lt;a name="_Hlk81406186"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
