&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In addition, some County Departments may have limited hours or will be lightly staffed on Friday, November 28, 2025.&amp;nbsp; Please call ahead of your visit on that day to see if the Department has staff available to assist you with your needs.&amp;nbsp; You can call (541) 672-3311 for general inquiries and Department extensions.&amp;nbsp; You can also log onto our website at &lt;a href="https://douglascountyor.gov/"&gt;https://douglascountyor.gov/&lt;/a&gt; to access the direct phone numbers for each County Department.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

